Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package is the collection of datasets in the format of relational events. Each dataset consists of an edgelist - the sequence events representing the link sent from one actor to another at a particular timepoint; and a dataframe describing the actors and their attributes if present. 
